        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1650",
        "content": "But I shall spare her.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1650_173552_000012_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1650/173552/1650_173552_000012_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1650",
        "content": "On the ancient monuments of barbarism and despotism I will inscribe great words of justice and mercy....",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1650_173552_000012_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1650/173552/1650_173552_000012_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1650",
        "content": "I do not wish to utilize the fortunes of war to humiliate an honored monarch.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1650_173552_000012_000017",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1650/173552/1650_173552_000012_000017.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1650",
        "content": "But can it be true that I am in Moscow?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1650_173552_000012_000018",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1650/173552/1650_173552_000012_000018.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1650",
        "content": "Yes, there she lies.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1650_173552_000015_000000",
