        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1650",
        "content": "The position was the more awkward because the Emperor, meditating upon his magnanimous plans, was pacing patiently up and down before the outspread map, occasionally glancing along the road to Moscow from under his lifted hand with a bright and proud smile.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
